(I've been helping my aunt move all this day, so when I got back I 
had about 300 messages to read. I've read them, and I realized 
something: Today the club had more fighting and confusion than any 
other day I've been here! KSLaw made a good point, about how we 
shouldn't be taking up space on the boad, especially fights. If 
you've got a problem with someone, send them a private e-mail. The 
rest of us don't need to know about it. So everybody just keep your 
cool and concentrate on the game. We're suppost to be having fun, 
remember? And I know I'm not the council or anything so this is just 
my opinion, but if you have something OOC that you really want to 
make sure that everybody reads, than combine it with a post. That 
wasy it will take up the same amount of space.)
